commit.message:
sh.h (SH_DBX_REGISTER_NUMBER): Added fpscr, fixed sr/gbr regs.

http://gcc.gnu.org/ml/gcc-patches/2007-09/msg00945.html
2007-09-12  Christian Bruel  <christian.bruel@st.com>
	* sh.h (SH_DBX_REGISTER_NUMBER): Added fpscr, fixed sr/gbr regs.
	* linux-unwind.h (SH_DWARF_FRAME_GBR): fixed.

From-SVN: r128413
